node.text:
Rice Pudding Magic :
- bring to the boil 1 cup of rice with 4 Cups of @almondbreezeaus Vanilla and 1 tsp of Vanilla extract. Cook for 20-40mins until liquid absorbs and and rice is tender.
- take off heat add 1/4 C of chia seeds and a cup of frozen blueberries stir through with some cinnamon, sea salt and Maple syrup to taste and eye ball a touch more @almondbreeze if more liquid is needed. Let stand for 15mins.
- Add yoghurt, fav toppings and your Magic Rice Pudding is complete. 
Ready for the day 🔥👊

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sally Fitzgibbons on September 15, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, ocean and text that says 'FITZGIBBONS 89'.

node.text:
So much to be thankful for after another lap around on the @wsl tour. Learnt…Loved…Lived 🙌💫
—————
Thank you to my loved ones, my team and everyone on the journey cheering me on to my goals in the 🇦🇺 #89 Jersey 🙏 Your love and support is in every wave I ride. I’m smiling right back at you : )
——————-
My amazing team of partners Thank you 🙌 @boostaus @all.pacific @underarmourau @breitling @landroveraus @sharpeyesurfboards_au @fcs_surf @devikaworld @axxeclassic @almondbreezeaus

node.text:
Amazing to experience history today with these incredible Surfers in the first ever @wsl Finals series 🙌💫
————-
Such an awesome atmosphere…huge thanks to the fans on the beach and around the world  for channelling some of your beautiful energy my way in such tough times 😷
—————-
Huge Congrats @rissmoore10 x5 and @gabrielmedina x3 to you and your teams on unbelievable seasons 🎉 🏆 
————————-
Powered by my amazing partners
@boostaus @breitling @all.pacific @underarmourau @landroveraus @devikaworld @fcs_surf @sharpeyesurfboards_au @axxeclassic @almondbreezeaus

node.text:
It was such an honour to represent my country with everything I had with our mighty @theirukandjis 🙏

It was so humbling to be a part of the Olympic class of #Tokyo2020 and amazing to to see the Sydney Opera House light up to celebrate all the incredible Olympic/Paraolympic Athletes!

Thank you to you all for supporting and cheering on our journeys 💚💛💚💛
